{"word":"σπεύδω","slug":"σπεύδω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>σπεύδω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> complex]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘proceed with haste’, of a <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> in rapid movement, <b>hurry <a href='B:490 2:16'>Lk 2:16</a>; <a href='B:490 19:5'>19:5f</a>; <a href='B:510 20:16'>Ac 20:16</a>; <a href='B:510 22:18'>22:18</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘cause to arrive earlier’, <b>hurry up, impel <a href='B:680 3:12'>2 Pt 3:12</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:σπερμολόγος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:σπήλαιον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}